{{!< default}}
{{! The tag above means - insert everything in this file into the {body} of the default.hbs template }}

{{! The big featured header }}

<header class="main-header {{#if @blog.cover}}" style="background-image: url({{@blog.cover}}){{else}}no-cover{{/if}}">
    <nav class="main-nav overlay clearfix">
        {{#if @blog.logo}}<a class="blog-logo" href="{{@blog.url}}"><img src="{{@blog.logo}}" alt="{{@blog.title}}" /></a>{{/if}}
        {{#if @blog.navigation}}
        {{/if}}
    </nav>
    <div id="hero" class="">
      <h1 class="page-title">{{@blog.title}}</h1>
      <h2 class="page-description">{{@blog.description}}</h2>
      <div class="download-button"><i class="fa fa-arrow-down"></i> Download files</div>
    </div>
    <a class="scroll-down icon-arrow-left" href="#content" data-offset="-45"><span class="hidden">Scroll Down</span></a>
</header>

{{! The main content area on the homepage }}
<main id="content" class="content" role="main">
    <div id="about-area">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <h2>The first open source 3D printable acoustic violin</h2>
          <p class="subtitle">That can cat sit for you while you are away.</p>
        </div>

        <p>The hovalin is a functional acoustic violin that can be produced using most standard consumer 3d printers. The total cost of raw materials for a Hovalin (4/4) is currently about $70.  The hovalin was designed with [Autodesk Fusion 360](fusion360.autodesk.com). It's shape and dimensions are inspired by the stradivarius violin model.</p>

        <p>There are three ways to get in on this: </p>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="do-it-area">
              <div class="icon-placeholder"></div>
              <h2>Print it</h2>
              <p>Well versed in 3D printing? Get the STL files and follow the instruction manual. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="do-it-area">
              <div class="icon-placeholder"></div>
              <h2>Get the kit</h2>
              <p>A fan of lego-like activities? Buy the kit and put the 3d printed parts together.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="do-it-area">
              <div class="icon-placeholder"></div>
              <h2>Buy it </h2>
              <p>Ainâ€™t nobody got time for all those other things. Get it fully assembled.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="video-area">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>See it in action</h2>
        <iframe width="100%" height="515" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dI4DpHnbX_Q" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{! The tag below includes the post loop - partials/loop.hbs }}
    <div id="blog-posts-area">
      <div class="container">
        {{> "loop"}}
      </div>
    </div>

</main>
